snippet.title: Through the Galaxy // Teaser
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/3108960/Through_the_Galaxy/

Immerse yourself in an unknown galaxy. Collect resources, upgrade your spaceship and experience an exciting mix of action and adventure with intense battles in a calm atmosphere. Discover new worlds and master challenges on your epic journey through space.

Developed by
Digital Datschi
